# URL of the live-score Cloudflare Worker (see worker/README.md).
# Leave unset to disable live in-match scores — the site then falls back to the
# periodic data refresh. Example:
# VITE_LIVE_API_URL=https://wc2026-live-scores.your-subdomain.workers.dev
VITE_LIVE_API_URL=https://wc2026-live-scores.xiidea.workers.dev
